## 🔧 Qwen-Optimized Structured Prompts for Background

As of KeyShot 2026.1, the Qwen model delivers stronger results with structured, attribute-based prompts. For Background Mode, the key fields are **ENVIRONMENT**, **LIGHTING**, **MATERIALS**, and **COLOR** — while SUBJECT is inherited from the existing product render.

### Structured Background Template

```
ENVIRONMENT: [setting type, spatial context, depth]
LIGHTING: [source, direction, softness, temperature, match to product]
MATERIALS: [ground surface, wall/backdrop textures, micro-detail]
COLOR: [dominant palette, accent tones, saturation level]
STYLE: [photographic style, realism level]
QUALITY: [detail, clarity, atmospheric depth]
EXCLUSIONS: [unwanted elements, clutter, distractions]
```

### Example: Premium Retail Display

**Structured:**
```
ENVIRONMENT: minimalist retail showroom with clean sightlines and receding depth
LIGHTING: soft overhead diffused light with warm accent spots, matched to product lighting direction
MATERIALS: polished light marble floor, smooth plaster wall, brushed brass shelf edge
COLOR: warm ivory, soft champagne, muted graphite accents
STYLE: architectural interior photography, clean commercial aesthetic
QUALITY: high realism, crisp surfaces, controlled atmospheric haze
EXCLUSIONS: no clutter, no branded signage, no people, no competing focal points
```

**Compiled:**
```
minimalist retail showroom with clean sightlines and receding depth, soft overhead diffused light with warm accent spots matched to product lighting direction, polished light marble floor with smooth plaster wall and brushed brass shelf edge, warm ivory and soft champagne palette with muted graphite accents, architectural interior photography with clean commercial aesthetic, high realism with crisp surfaces and controlled atmospheric haze, no clutter no branded signage no people no competing focal points
```

### Example: Rugged Outdoor Context

**Structured:**
```
ENVIRONMENT: mountain trail overlook at golden hour with layered terrain
LIGHTING: golden backlight from low sun, soft ambient fill from open sky, long warm shadows
MATERIALS: weathered granite, packed dirt trail, sparse dry grass, distant pine bark
COLOR: warm amber, dusty ochre, muted forest green, pale sky blue
STYLE: outdoor editorial photography, natural realism
QUALITY: atmospheric depth, natural detail, soft background falloff
EXCLUSIONS: no vehicles, no people, no structures, no artificial objects
```

